sequenceDiagram
    participant O as Operator
    participant C as Console (SpecCanvas)
    participant R as POST /api/runtime/tasks
    participant H as Harness (Antigravity)
    participant S as Spec store

    O->>C: start interview, provide brief + BRD
    C->>R: runtimeStart(harness.run)
    R->>H: launch interview run
    loop streaming spec
        H-->>C: artifact identifier="agent-spec" chunk
        C-->>O: canvas renders workflow / answerable queries incrementally
    end
    O->>C: edit + confirm spec
    C->>S: POST /api/interviews/:id/spec
    O->>S: GET /api/interviews/:id/okf
    S-->>O: OKF Knowledge Bundle (files, conceptCount)
